  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had to-- to take-- take the chance myself to walk out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, it took-- it was-- it was in-- in Sunday that I pocketed the [INAUDIBLE] things that I had, the Napoleon gold, some of it, and left the-- the house, left with Mrs.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Tigany.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was about 200 [NON-ENGLISH], at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could buy a cow with Napoleon gold at-- at the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, the necessary papers what I had-- not so secured false paper, and out to the Western station to-- to find out-- to find out about-- about the-- the train schedule, out of-- back to-- back [INAUDIBLE], where I-- where came in.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was-- that was on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that I can either come back to Mrs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Tigany, or to spend the night somewhere else and go-- and go Monday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But on-- I went into the restaurant on the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was [INAUDIBLE] boulevard in-- in Budapest, not very far from the Western-- Western station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at about 1 o'clock, when I was just finishing my dinner in the restaurant on the corner of a street in the main-- main boulevard there-- at 1 o'clock everything-- the radio stopped, the music on it.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it stopped and announced that Miklos Horthy, the Regent of-- of Hungary, has a message to.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he-- he said a, so to say, a bullshit talk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was actually a provocation, not a-- and not to help, that we are-- we are planning or considering to side with the other side, with the Allies, and so on and so forth, refuting the-- which would actually expose the Hungarian military leadership.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because many of them took it for granted what was in the air already, waiting for the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
